@UniversityTasksDbFirstApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:7243

### Courses (all)
GET {{UniversityTasksDbFirstApi_HostAddress}}/api/courses

### Courses (active only)
GET {{UniversityTasksDbFirstApi_HostAddress}}/api/courses?activeOnly=true

### Assignments for course 1 (published only)
GET {{UniversityTasksDbFirstApi_HostAddress}}/api/courses/1/assignments?publishedOnly=true

### Student dashboard
GET {{UniversityTasksDbFirstApi_HostAddress}}/api/students/1/dashboard

### Create submission
POST {{UniversityTasksDbFirstApi_HostAddress}}/api/submissions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assignmentId": 3,
  "studentId": 5,
  "repositoryUrl": "https://github.com/student/performance-review"
}

### Grade submission
PUT {{UniversityTasksDbFirstApi_HostAddress}}/api/submissions/5/grade
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 23,
  "feedback": "Correct use of projections and AsNoTracking. Please improve error messages."
}

### Delete submission
DELETE {{UniversityTasksDbFirstApi_HostAddress}}/api/submissions/5
